# demo.tape — VHS tape for citedhealth CLI demo GIF
# Generate with: vhs demo.tape

Output demo.gif

Set FontSize 20
Set Width 1000
Set Height 580
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set TypingSpeed 30ms
Set Padding 24

Type "citedhealth ingredients biotin"
Enter
Sleep 3s

Type "citedhealth evidence biotin nutritional-deficiency-hair-loss"
Enter
Sleep 3s

Type "citedhealth papers --year 2024"
Enter
Sleep 3s
